Cave eels are a type of food that can be obtained by cooking a raw cave eel on a fire or cooking range, requiring level 38 Cooking and granting 115 experience when successful. Players may burn a cave eel while cooking one, resulting in a burnt cave eel; the burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning entirely at Cooking level 74 on both ranges and fires.

When eaten, a cave eel will restore 8 to 12 hitpoints. They are used in several quests that require the gathering of objects. Raw cave eel are used in the Creature Creation minigame to make a frogeel.
